title: Live on a quiet tree-lined block in the heart of Midtown Detroit
posting_body: Live on a quiet tree-lined block in the heart of Midtown Detroit.
Our spacious fully renovated studios and one-bedroom apartments are complete with modern updates, hardwood floors, and ample natural light.
Laundry is conveniently onsite, and dogs and cats are welcome!
Your new home lets you take full advantage of a booming neighborhood, with amazing restaurants, great nightlife, and boutique shopping all a short walk away.
Live minutes from Wayne State University, The College for Create Studies, The DMC, and the M-1 Rail Line.
You are truly living in the middle of it all when you call Villa Lante home.
